{
  "texts": [
    "We hope our work provides valuable insights into the application of abstractive summarization for scientific papers.",
    "Meanwhile, we notice that the proposed two-stage framework could be optimized by exploring alternative backbones.",
    "In our future research, more advanced LLM will be investigated for structure information extraction and abstractive summarization to further enhance performance.",
    "Although SciBERT achieved notably better results on the arXiv dataset, the overlapping confidence intervals on the PubMed dataset indicate no statistically significant differences between SciBERT, T5-base, and RoBERTa in certain cases.",
    "In light of these results, we further investigated the training efficiency of these models to assess their practicality for large-scale tasks."
  ]
}